{"tid":709533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日搭地鐵見到條女著到咁","createTime":"2018-06-20T05:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T10:51:30.000Z","uid":69898,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1c056f13fa82fa5e9730fe36dcf3e9feb87de7","tid":709533,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:35:13.000Z","msg":"條女著白色露臍小背心(比示意圖更露得多肉)，再加件oversize恤衫，所以永遠露一邊肩，下身配短牛仔褲，白滑美腿出哂黎<br />\n<br />\n佢個男朋友仲好似好開心咁<br />\n人地女朋友著到咁，就緊係覺得好正<br />\n但自己女朋友著到咁，你接唔接受到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n示意圖(from 淘寶)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/132953_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F132953_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=17ad2c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/133002_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F133002_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8fc1528e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb88033b83b0df3d9ba03b1715a07c8cc534dc3a","tid":709533,"uid":149831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"點會接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c724b1e94eac2ac92e5b6739a392e9b77334be","tid":709533,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb88033b83b0df3d9ba03b1715a07c8cc534dc3a","tid":709533,"uid":149831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"點會接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"女朋友係咁比人視姦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 望左一眼，就訓咗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"